name: DAODenver (by DAOPlanet)
description:
We’re raising funds to Make DAODenver Free to all ETHDenver attendees!

DAOPlanet.org (prev. DAOists.xyz) is hosting DAODenver on Feb. 15 & 16, as part of ETHDenver’s “Buidl” week.

When goal is reached ($250K) DAODenver is FREE (w/ ticket holders offered refunds – risk-free purchase now guarantees entry).
If goal is not met, all funds still go to reducing attendee costs.

Excess funds go to DAOPlanet efforts helping people & organizations unlock their potential within Decentralized Autonomous Organizations. DAOPlanet’s vision is greater representation for individuals within communities, organizations, businesses, and the entire world — achieved through the integration and proliferation of DAO principles and Web3 tools.

DAOPlanet tokens are for governance and utility within its community. Join our Discord: https://bit.ly/DAOPlanet

DAOPlanet reserves right to mint native tokens such that tokens issued through this campaign equal no more than 15% of total tokens.
